{
  "page": "House Qoherys",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold\">House Qoherys of Harrenhal</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Qoherys.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Qoherys.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/52/House_Qoherys.svg/250px-House_Qoherys.svg.png\" width=\"250\" height=\"275\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/52/House_Qoherys.svg/375px-House_Qoherys.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/52/House_Qoherys.svg/500px-House_Qoherys.svg.png 2x\" /></a><div></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Coat of arms</th><td>\nA flaming saltire, red and yellow, between 4 white skulls, on black<br />(<i>Sable, a saltire rayonné gules and or, between four skulls argent</i>)</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Seat</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Harrenhal\" title=\"Harrenhal\">Harrenhal</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Head</th><td>\nExtinct</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Region</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">Riverlands</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Harrenhal\" title=\"Lord of Harrenhal\">Lord of Harrenhal</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Overlord</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Tully\" title=\"House Tully\">House Tully</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Founder</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Quenton_Qoherys\" title=\"Quenton Qoherys\">Quenton Qoherys</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Founded</th><td>\nca. <a href=\"/index.php/1_AC\" title=\"1 AC\">1&#160;AC</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died out</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/37_AC\" title=\"37 AC\">37&#160;AC</a> or shortly after</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>House Qoherys of Harrenhal</b> is an extinct noble house from <a href=\"/index.php/Harrenhal\" title=\"Harrenhal\">Harrenhal</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">riverlands</a>. They blazoned their arms with a flaming saltire, red and yellow, between four white skulls, on black.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Qoherys&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>According to a semi-canon source, House Qoherys was of <a href=\"/index.php/Valyria\" title=\"Valyria\">Valyrian</a> descent.<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Quenton_Qoherys\" title=\"Quenton Qoherys\">Quenton Qoherys</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Master-at-arms\" title=\"Master-at-arms\">master-at-arms</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonstone\" title=\"Dragonstone\">Dragonstone</a>, was granted the ruined castle of <a href=\"/index.php/Harrenhal\" title=\"Harrenhal\">Harrenhal</a> by King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon I Targaryen\">Aegon I Targaryen</a>, as <a href=\"/index.php/House_Hoare\" title=\"House Hoare\">House Hoare</a> was extinguished in the <a href=\"/index.php/Burning_of_Harrenhal\" title=\"Burning of Harrenhal\">burning of Harrenhal</a> during <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon%27s_Conquest\" title=\"Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">Aegon's Conquest</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon_-_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon_-_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> Quenton was succeeded by his grandson, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Gargon_Qoherys\" title=\"Gargon Qoherys\">Gargon the Guest</a>, who was murdered in the rebellion of <a href=\"/index.php/Harren_the_Red\" title=\"Harren the Red\">Harren the Red</a> during the reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aenys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aenys I Targaryen\">Aenys I Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Harroway\" title=\"House Harroway\">House Harroway</a> was then granted the lands and incomes of Harrenhal.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_riverlands:_house_tully.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_riverlands:_house_tully.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Historical_Members\">Historical Members</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Qoherys&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Historical Members\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Quenton_Qoherys\" title=\"Quenton Qoherys\">Quenton Qoherys</a>, founder of the house.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_riverlands:_house_tully.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_riverlands:_house_tully.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n<ul><li>His first wife, who died to spotted fever.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon_-_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon_-_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n<ul><li>Two sons.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon_-_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon_-_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n<ul><li>His grandson Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Gargon_Qoherys\" title=\"Gargon Qoherys\">Gargon Qoherys</a>, called Gargon the Guest, the last of the house.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></li></ul></li></ul></li>\n<li>His second wife, a daughter of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Edmyn_Tully\" title=\"Edmyn Tully\">Edmyn Tully</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Riverrun\" title=\"Riverrun\">Riverrun</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_riverlands:_house_tully.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_riverlands:_house_tully.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></li></ul></li></ul>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\">Unknown<br />first wife</td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Quenton_Qoherys\" title=\"Quenton Qoherys\">Quenton</a></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black;\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\">Daughter of<br /><a 